				<h2 class="heading--2">Replacing Multiple Tools With a Single Solution</h2>

				<p class="paragraph--2">To enhance its operational security, CKB deployed Qualys Vulnerability Management – an enterprise-class, cloud-based solution – to map all assets and identify potential vulnerabilities.</p>


