				<h2 class="heading--2">Ensuring Regulatory Compliance</h2>

				<p class="paragraph--2">Today, CKB uses the Qualys solution to generate Common Vulnerability Scoring System (CVSS) metrics for each of its systems. These scores help the company to assess vulnerability and prioritize the relevant remediation activities.</p>


				<p class="paragraph--2">Saša Šćekić comments: <b><i>“The solution enables us to perform comprehensive scans without impacting the performance and availability of key systems. We can fine-tune our vulnerability scans to minimize the number of false positives, and overall, we are seeing accurate results.”</i></b></p>

